Description: This is a really cool daphne blue 2018 Fender Limited Edition American Professional Stratocaster featuring a completely rosewood neck and headstock. The guitar is in fantastic condition. Honestly, you can buy a brand new one (if you can find one) but I doubt you could tell the difference from this one. This guitar is virtually unused.
